# AI Clipping System

Modular local-first backend for converting long-form videos into short vertical clips with Whisper, Ollama, FFmpeg, and FastAPI.

## Architecture

```text
User
  |
  v
FastAPI API
  |
  v
Processing Job Queue
  |
  v
Video Processing Pipeline
  |- Video Downloader
  |- Audio Extractor
  |- Speech Transcriber
  |- Viral Moment Detector
  |- Clip Generator
  |- Subtitle Generator
  `- Export Manager
```

